Like after being in design

00:02:26.226 --> 00:02:27.836
school making handmade books for example.

00:02:27.836 --> 00:02:30.439
Like 4 x 6 little book
would be really sweet.

00:02:30.439 --> 00:02:32.246
I was like really excited
and jazzed about this.

00:02:32.246 --> 00:02:37.393
Then as I started in
2007 to 2009, it was you

00:02:37.393 --> 00:02:39.282
have the iPad, iPhone,
all these technological

00:02:39.282 --> 00:02:41.683
advances just happen
while I'm in grad school.

00:02:41.683 --> 00:02:43.685
I will have to rethink this a little.

00:02:43.685 --> 00:02:45.114
I got this design degree.

00:02:45.114 --> 00:02:46.292
Interviewer: From [Risty].

00:02:46.292 --> 00:02:47.299
Marcos: From [Risty].

00:02:47.299 --> 00:02:49.727
Interviewer: That's a serious
design school. That's around there.

00:02:49.727 --> 00:02:51.957
Marcos: I had did my
grad program in design.

