ended up being my thesis was ...

00:03:08.727 --> 00:03:10.344
Interviewer: How many
CS majors were there?

00:03:10.344 --> 00:03:14.523
Marcos: Actually, when I
left there was 1 and a half.

00:03:14.523 --> 00:03:16.482
Interviewer: 1 and a half. (laughing)

00:03:16.482 --> 00:03:19.149
Marcos: It's an up and coming thing.

00:03:19.149 --> 00:03:21.751
Interviewer: Yeah. I think
