00:03:25.556 --> 00:03:29.038
Marcos: Yeah. Exactly.
What I noticed, at least,

00:03:29.038 --> 00:03:33.001
there was a lot of similarity.
The Christopher Alexander design

00:03:33.001 --> 00:03:35.896
patterns thinking. That
system thinking, actually,

00:03:35.896 --> 00:03:37.818
