00:04:49.733 --> 00:04:52.537
Marcos: Yeah. Carnegie Mellon.
Human-Computer Interaction Institute.

00:04:52.537 --> 00:04:53.184
Interviewer: Okay.

00:04:53.184 --> 00:04:57.199
Marcos: With Laura Dabbish and
