What does that feel like?

00:07:25.250 --> 00:07:29.218
A lot of these are very
designish things that

00:07:29.218 --> 00:07:30.975
we're probing, but we
ended up coming up with

00:07:30.975 --> 00:07:33.337
a very ... and he actually
deserves most of the

00:07:33.337 --> 00:07:35.920
