00:07:58.670 --> 00:08:01.005
how far you're doing? Which of these ...

00:08:01.005 --> 00:08:03.647
Interviewer: How doing means you
actually belief in how your doing.

00:08:03.647 --> 00:08:06.755
Marcos: Exactly. A lot
of that your questions of

00:08:06.755 --> 00:08:09.699
would it feel better as
your gaining proficiency?

