was very more metro rigorous.

00:08:23.357 --> 00:08:26.621
Then like back and forths
that we were having

00:08:26.621 --> 00:08:28.227
initially when we sketching it out.

00:08:28.227 --> 00:08:31.058
Interviewer: Where do you hope this goes?

00:08:31.058 --> 00:08:35.474
Marcos: I think, recently,
I've been spending

00:08:35.474 --> 00:08:38.638
